{"tid":278322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做札鐵既麻煩請進","createTime":"2017-06-10T10:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T06:54:59.000Z","uid":117440,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb7141329e39ceacef4f2a45e21a2ddd6c235c79","tid":278322,"uid":117440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T10:47:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我男友係做札鐵既<br />\n呢排佢掉咗去無雷公咁遠既開料場<br />\n所以早咗半個鐘收工 ，即5點<br />\n但同時佢間唔中就話開夜<br />\n開多兩三個鐘咁<br />\n佢之前又因為做錯某啲事(呃我唔只一次）<br />\n搞到我唔知信唔信佢好<br />\n所以好想問下各位真漢子<br />\n開料場係咪真係會留人夜麻麻開料#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係好想信佢 但佢誠信好一般<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叉開少少 <br />\n我覺得一個人既誠信真係好重要 <br />\n起碼為世所逼時講一個半個大話都仲有人會信你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n依家唔信佢搞到好似係我疑心大咁 <br />\n但我以前同人拍拖係放心到叫佢地出去揾fd玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1b705aa2bdf111d6c090be28f2d1719d437c9a","tid":278322,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T10:52:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"266341d2c8a2d663cecf5986c199e002aeb7fb11","tid":278322,"uid":36754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T10:53:14.000Z","msg":"扎鐵咁辛苦又搵咁多 唔叫雞就假既"},{"pid":"41adc96589bad98b5d62676ab30bfb4d09e4452b","tid":278322,"uid":28695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:01:40.000Z","msg":"地盤夜晚趕工落石屎見得多，但18:00過後仲可以見到紥鐵佬做野就一次都未見過<br />\n<br />\nbtw,冇事既收工去發洩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2088841cd5d63c38602b1f7eb1dfbfbbe7b2e66","tid":278322,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:04:09.000Z","msg":"佢叫雞<br />\n呢個答案滿意未"},{"pid":"d4b25bdeb5fed31b4908a34c66cac0a8c5779b35","tid":278322,"uid":71473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"叫雞姐，好閑！"},{"pid":"c519a7a4c122c9994ba1f17176ed82b593e8d223","tid":278322,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"馮場作興姐<br />\n<br />\n師傅叫到唔通唔去咩<br />\n<br />\nPs:我未見過呢樣人唔嫖<br />\n<br />\n唔想唔開心就唔好現場等佢收工"},{"pid":"5bf30ffc63a9d65f5ed9a1b6f9616f295bd8a83a","tid":278322,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:10:34.000Z","msg":"5點去開苞"},{"pid":"19e0f04f82511ca2f2a43b739d6cf9aea5490ba3","tid":278322,"uid":55847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:10:41.000Z","msg":"叫雞/第個"},{"pid":"5dc143037962575b947fa47e8da8a7087a0fd29f","tid":278322,"uid":69064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:44:48.000Z","msg":"紮鐵佬4:30就收工啦"},{"pid":"ca08de120b109555e69c5078ff2ae815cfc48d71","tid":278322,"uid":23828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"趕起貨最盡7點"},{"pid":"48db8106f3b696a173884ed6bfaa9df62b16a146","tid":278322,"uid":117440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:50:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地盤夜晚趕工落石屎見得多，但18:00過後仲可以見到紥鐵佬做野就一次都未見過<br />\n<br />\nbtw,冇事既收工去發洩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都覺得係叫雞<br />\n但叫雞會唔會為咗唔留證據特登唔沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢收工返黎個身仲係污糟"},{"pid":"db02d6c0de73d1be2039036b3f7879db5be45610","tid":278322,"uid":117440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:52:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>趕起貨最盡7點</blockquote><br />\n佢頭先8點鐘收工，話係有人做錯野要執尾"},{"pid":"ce4a8619ddb4bb527f6dce5145aea96a4ba7c64b","tid":278322,"uid":117440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:54:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馮場作興姐<br />\n<br />\n師傅叫到唔通唔去咩<br />\n<br />\nPs:我未見過呢樣人唔嫖<br />\n<br />\n唔想唔開心就唔好現場等佢收工</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪同行？<br />\n其實係咪真係十個地盤佬十個都去嫖？<br />\n咁你係咪都會嫖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47fb7385a92b61daaf358249a1373e543094ed3","tid":278322,"uid":30991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:54:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>趕起貨最盡7點</blockquote><br />\n佢頭先8點鐘收工，話係有人做錯野要執尾</blockquote><br />\n7:00 有人做錯野 要同隻雞執尾 咪8:00收工"},{"pid":"8968b8b314ad5bf66af60fb164d5e6109c23509a","tid":278322,"uid":55614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:56:32.000Z","msg":"下午去叫雞 夜晚先去做野 番到屋企個身咪污糟囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你信就點講都會信 唔信就點講都唔會信架啦"},{"pid":"1faf70c74b6f0c276e96228fb2603570ba8fb3ed","tid":278322,"uid":106093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下午去叫雞 夜晚先去做野 番到屋企個身咪污糟囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你信就點講都會信 唔信就點講都唔會信架啦</blockquote><br />\n岩呀 一句講哂 信定唔信<br />\n唔信咩都係籍口<br />\n <br />\n利申 地盤佬 開夜7、8點經常有"},{"pid":"a6da7b3bf021c70f57f59aafbed196f103097ba8","tid":278322,"uid":117440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下午去叫雞 夜晚先去做野 番到屋企個身咪污糟囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你信就點講都會信 唔信就點講都唔會信架啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你又岩 咁我當佢係叫雞啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係人都愛新鮮 我明<br />\n但有女友都唔識珍惜我就唔明<br />\n睇黎我一係離開佢<br />\n一係學做個壞女人"},{"pid":"74f7cf0d003aaf343f6006ccaed8bff5c27159ec","tid":278322,"uid":117440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:38:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下午去叫雞 夜晚先去做野 番到屋企個身咪污糟囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你信就點講都會信 唔信就點講都唔會信架啦</blockquote><br />\n岩呀 一句講哂 信定唔信<br />\n唔信咩都係籍口<br />\n <br />\n利申 地盤佬 開夜7、8點經常有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你巴打，祝你工作事事順利，同埋唔好去嫖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d7f27ce99dc0bd7e312acb1fffb112cdfa6611","tid":278322,"uid":18980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:41:52.000Z","msg":"男友做搭棚 ot到11點都會有<br />\n信 唔係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac7bb55f5f201d13912e6cf9bc89b12df4c182f","tid":278322,"uid":106930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男友做搭棚 ot到11點都會有<br />\n信 唔係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n11點搭棚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵鬼信"},{"pid":"6c21fcd78e06f1dc2890162440312eaa9532990e","tid":278322,"uid":52483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:51:08.000Z","msg":"你咪叫鴨囉去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c095408fb96693ab9211a56ef46826d3ed4bc5fd","tid":278322,"uid":53510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:55:23.000Z","msg":"有時啲工程地方 好鄰近市中心，有好多商夏，商場都唔比工程日間開工，開夜有幾咁奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2437dc90698608d161d0aaa1642588d79fa4f5c9","tid":278322,"uid":15862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:08:12.000Z","msg":"我做兒童醫院個盤 趕起貨都晚晚9點收工<br />\n你想拎個明白咪叫佢影一張相囉 一張相唔係咁難姐 開個whatsapp都有粒制比佢撳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef58a0fa81a0ad1c753463207fcaa19e68ecd38","tid":278322,"uid":55847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下午去叫雞 夜晚先去做野 番到屋企個身咪污糟囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你信就點講都會信 唔信就點講都唔會信架啦</blockquote><br />\n岩呀 一句講哂 信定唔信<br />\n唔信咩都係籍口<br />\n <br />\n利申 地盤佬 開夜7、8點經常有</blockquote><br />\n認同   條友根本揾人安慰佢條仔無叫雞<br />\n哂人時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c108b8a760c1b18cd4466d2e5dcd517852cd7751","tid":278322,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:35:58.000Z","msg":"一定係去左叫雞啦！！你平時望下啲有粉紅色燈既唐樓 好多後生仔出出入入架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c604d9fc14cc9769f0312fc95ff2aa3194852010","tid":278322,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"其實我又唔係好信地盤無基佬"},{"pid":"3bf55ccee5eaa604eea3f849138ca51edc69ebf9","tid":278322,"uid":97708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:51:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>男友做搭棚 ot到11點都會有<br />\n信 唔係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n11點搭棚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵鬼信</blockquote><br />\n仆撚死左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2ec84a5ee80cf33673dfde1872c9f401eb0ee9","tid":278322,"uid":18980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:19:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>男友做搭棚 ot到11點都會有<br />\n信 唔係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n11點搭棚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵鬼信</blockquote><br />\n仆撚死左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係圓方個邊 唔知啊 得個信字"},{"pid":"6193da68e8ed12ab950ce624dfe922967e2c7091","tid":278322,"uid":117440,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>下午去叫雞 夜晚先去做野 番到屋企個身咪污糟囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你信就點講都會信 唔信就點講都唔會信架啦</blockquote><br />\n岩呀 一句講哂 信定唔信<br />\n唔信咩都係籍口<br />\n <br />\n利申 地盤佬 開夜7、8點經常有</blockquote><br />\n認同   條友根本揾人安慰佢條仔無叫雞<br />\n哂人時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係相反<br />\n我係預咗大家會話佢去咗叫雞<br />\n當有咁多人認同自己我反而覺得䆁懷<br />\n唔洗再對佢咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慢慢心息然後離開"},{"pid":"4074a7a057b3ba1c2181ef1c8708f25e9542587b","tid":278322,"uid":117440,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:29:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咪叫鴨囉去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不了 太污糟了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果真係要你做初一我做十五<br />\n我會傾向扮好女人 呃哂佢啲錢 再飛咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68d6b2892cd50ef92f9f4fdd311b99929db81e0","tid":278322,"uid":53018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:33:30.000Z","msg":"其實 一啲唔近住宅 嘅地盤 我見過夜晚都會有人做野"},{"pid":"55c402dc414a3a518508c5386002d905f8bd279a","tid":278322,"uid":117440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男友做搭棚 ot到11點都會有<br />\n信 唔係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 黑麻麻搭棚好危險<br />\n但你都仲信佢證明佢係可信既人<br />\n有一段互相信任既關係真係好<br />\n要好好珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d65da36181f2150240ca25701fe7bb1917649a","tid":278322,"uid":8302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:40:04.000Z","msg":"5點就收工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係 唔知佢係唔係"},{"pid":"b894af182f0248f474767431833cbd5390508c1a","tid":278322,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:40:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>男友做搭棚 ot到11點都會有<br />\n信 唔係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 黑麻麻搭棚好危險<br />\n但你都仲信佢證明佢係可信既人<br />\n有一段互相信任既關係真係好<br />\n要好好珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9先信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己去望下法定規管左是時間係幾點至幾點先啦"},{"pid":"287e038bebb53e